BUILD AND INSTALL: UBUNTU
-------------------------

1. Requirements
It is required that gimptool is installed.
On an Ubuntu PC this is installed by:

$ sudo apt-get install libgimp2.0-dev

2. Make

$ make				will compile the plugins
$ make install			will install the plugins locally
$ make uninstall		will uninstall the plugins from local install
				directory
$ sudo make install-admin	will install the plugin in the Gimp install
				directory
$ sudo make uninstall-admin	will uninstall the plugin from the Gimp install
				directory
